data.description: One-story home. Move-In Ready located in a Gated Community with a Lake, and playground.     The home has an Office w French Doors, Peninsula Kitchen, Covered Patio with a HUGE YARD and STORAGE SHED, the Master Bath Features a Walk In Shower.        There are tile floors throughout the living areas, with carpet in the bedrooms. A Refrigerator will be included.        Easy drive to Lackland, with quick on/access to Hwy 151 & Loop 410.
